; Regression test for issue #749: Value expression parser confused by ( ) in commodity name (BZ#749)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/749
;
; When a commodity name contains parentheses (e.g. "XYZ (Bond)"), the value
; expression parser could be confused by the parens, treating them as expression
; grouping operators rather than part of the commodity name.

2024/01/01 Buy Bonds
    Assets:Investments    10 "XYZ (Bond)"
    Equity

test bal
       10 XYZ (Bond)  Assets:Investments
      -10 XYZ (Bond)  Equity
--------------------
                   0
end test

test reg
24-Jan-01 Buy Bonds             Assets:Investments     10 XYZ (Bond) 10 XYZ (Bond)
                                Equity                 -10 XYZ (Bond)            0
end test

test reg --format "%(commodity)\n"
XYZ (Bond)
XYZ (Bond)
end test
